content: @text mod Hello, how do I update my phone # that I used to register?  I want to use my Google Voice # instead of my actual cell #?
Hi Lisa! Thanks for posting your questions here! I am tagging <@477560366432256000> who should be able to help you!
You would have to contact scale to win regarding that. I'll give you there info in an direct message.
Thanks Jack!  I have not received anything from Scale to Win yet, should I have by now?
Nope. I need to find there contact info.
I attended the training and registered yesterday
<@477560366432256000> Keep me posted, I’ll check back later this evening.  Thanks!

Hi <@1279572054818947108> , you may know this already, but when texting with our campaign, the recipients never see your phone number. If you are able to login to democrats.text.scaletowin.com/ you can go to your profile and edit your phone number. Click the Initial in upper right hand corner, then click on your name to get to your profile.
I sent them that but thanks Laura.
Hi <@756314488113987654>  I did not know this.  I will goin to the link.  <@477560366432256000> where did you send, I don’t find a link from you here in chats nor in email?
I sent you an direct message to update your display name. That's the first step.
Thanks <@477560366432256000> .  I was able to update.  I am waiting for Scale To Win ‘registration to complete.
